        <li style="font-size: 16pt">Reduce risks of suicidality</li>
        <li style="font-size: 16pt">Promote mental health wellness 24/7</li>
        <li style="font-size: 16pt">Enable better information sharing  between your Counseling Center and your local mental health referral network</li>
        <li style="font-size: 16pt">More accurate data on mental health condition on campus</li>
        <li style="font-size: 16pt">Unique data collection tool for clinical research that does not exist anywhere else</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
    <br><br>
    <%= image_tag('patient_centered2.png' ) %>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
    <h2>What our tool provides</h2>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h3>For Students:</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
    <div class="image">
      <%= image_tag('hands.png', size: "200x200") %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8" style="margin-left: 20px">
    <h3>Taking ownership of their mental health.
    </h3>
    <p>
      Students can start tracking their moods, symptoms, cravings, energy level, and other key indicators that can help identify potential diagnosed conditions. Instead of one-time screening assessments which often miss mood and behavior swings, Faro10 allows students to track their mental health 24/7, which provides a better picture of their mental health. Even if the student decides that their condition is not concerning enough to see a professional, they have taken the step to become far more aware of their mental health and how it impacts their life.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>



<div class="row"><br>
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
    <div class="image">
      <%= image_tag('phone1.png', size: "180x180" ) %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8" style="margin-left: 20px">
    <h3>Better information for diagnosis and treatment.
    </h3>
    <p>
      If they decide to see a professional counselor, they can accelerate diagnosis and the treatment process because they will bring a history of
      their mental health data that is otherwise unavailable.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">  <br>
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
    <div class="image">
      <%= image_tag('report.png', size: "190x190") %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-md-8" style="margin-left: 20px">
    <h3>Smoother care transition.
    </h3>
    <p>
      If students need professional help while in college, it makes a lot of sense to make sure that their new care providers can easily connect with their previous,
      home-town care providers. Faro10 enables all care providers, regardless of location, employer, practice, or IT system to get a more comprehensive report on their patients.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


